                            <comment id="14467496" author="roshandawrani" created="Mon, 31 Aug 2009 23:18:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed. Pattern check against null now throws NPE and is consistent with Java.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14467612" author="roshandawrani" created="Fri, 4 Sep 2009 12:48:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Discussion on the dev list brought out that returning false was a much suitable result compared to NPE. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;NPE behavior introduced in pass-1 fix created an issue with Gant build that was using null ==~ something kind of pattern matching in some cases.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
